Summary: 3 dark dark red orbs and solid center.
divs: sighting detailsi was just walking my dog when i saw a shooting star. it caught my eye so i looked up into the sky to see if i could see more of them. then something else caught my eye. it was a dark mass with 3 very dark red orbs or dark areas that appeared to be orbs went over. i could not see the craft but i could see it blocking out the stars behind it. i could make out that it was a triangle shape but no detail to it other then the 3 dark reddish orbs. the object made no sound at all and it moved smooth like a disc on a table hockey board. i watched it fly past until it was out of site. i have attached a image i made of what i saw. the background is just some random pic i found on the web. the sky was\ is much darker then in the image but it represents what i am tyring to show.
